# Build context is projects/ (parent of CI/). Prune heavy or sensitive trees.

**/.git/objects
**/.git/logs
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/.venv
**/.boot-linux
**/.boot-macos
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/dist
**/build
**/.pytest_cache
**/.coverage
**/.mypy_cache
**/.ruff_cache

# Large non-wiki artifacts in CI
CI/*.pdf
CI/.venv
CI/china-interim-measures-genai.pdf
CI/unesco-ai-ethics-recommendation.pdf
CI/us-ai-bill-of-rights.pdf

# Dev-only wiki state (feedback is a runtime volume in prod)
CI/web/data/feedback